likely he's a horse's ass.

56:20.546 --> 56:23.179
Uh, Dr. Dreessen,
this is Dr. Masters.

56:23.215 --> 56:25.782
- You already know Dr. Leveau.
- A pleasure.

56:25.817 --> 56:27.417
Of course.

56:27.452 --> 56:29.185
Dr. Masters and I
have been going over

56:29.221 --> 56:31.021
